WEZTERM CHEATSHEET

USAGE: wezterm [command] [options]
       Leader: Ctrl+a

APPLICATION CONTROL:
  Cmd+q                       Quit WezTerm
  Cmd+K                       Clear screen and flash
  Cmd+/                       Search current content
  Leader+h                    Command palette
  Leader+d                    Debug interface
  Leader+c                    Launch menu
  Leader+?                    Show cheatsheets

FONT & DISPLAY:
  Cmd+=                       Increase font size
  Cmd+-                       Decrease font size
  Cmd+0                       Reset font size

WORKSPACE MANAGEMENT:
  Leader+s                    Workspace selector
  Leader+w                    Create New Workspace
  Leader+l                    Switch to last workspace
  Cmd+Opt+[                   Previous workspace
  Cmd+Opt+]                   Next workspace
  Leader+Shift+$              Rename current workspace

TAB MANAGEMENT:
  Cmd+T                       New tab
  Cmd+W                       Close current tab
  Cmd+1-9                     Jump to tab by number
  Cmd+Shift+[                 Previous tab
  Cmd+Shift+]                 Next tab
  Leader+,                    Rename current tab
  Leader+t                    Tab selector (fuzzy search)

PANE MANAGEMENT:
  Split:
  Leader+-                    Split vertically (top/bottom)
  Leader+\                    Split horizontally (left/right)
  Leader+z                    Toggle pane zoom

  Navigation:
  Cmd+Opt+←→↑↓                Navigate panes by direction
  Leader+m → s                Pane selector

MODAL OPERATIONS:
  Copy Mode (Leader+y):
  b                           Copy entire buffer
  p                           Copy current page
  l                           Smart line copy
  r                           Regex copy (IPs, emails, URLs, etc)

  Open Mode (Leader+o):
  p                           Open Finder in current directory
  c                           Open VS Code
  u                           Open URL from screen

  Move Mode (Leader+m):
  r                           Rotate panes counter-clockwise
  s                           Pane selector
  Shift+←→                    Move tab position

  Resize Mode (Leader+r):
  ←                           Expand left (1 char)
  →                           Expand right (1 char)
  ↑                           Expand up (1 line)
  ↓                           Expand down (1 line)
  Enter/Esc                   Exit resize mode

COPY & PASTE:
  Cmd+C / Double-click        Copy selected text
  Cmd+V / Right-click         Paste clipboard content
  Triple-click                Select entire line
  Leader+v                    Enter vim-style copy mode

SCROLLING:
  Shift+↑↓                    Line scroll (1 line)
  Cmd+Shift+↑↓                Page scroll (1 page)
  Cmd+Opt+↑↓                  Half page scroll (0.5 page)
  Cmd+↑                       Scroll to top
  Cmd+↓                       Scroll to bottom

CONFIGURATION:
  Config location:            ~/.config/wezterm/
  Launch items:               config/launch.lua
  Workspaces:                 utils/workspaces.lua
  Cheatsheets:                ~/.dotfiles/cheatsheets/

